OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of an
OL,6,Fisolated shower or thunderstorm during
OL,7,Fthe evening, otherwise a fine and
OL,8,Fmainly dry night with clear spells.
OL,9,FBecoming cloudy around dawn with
OL,10,Fpatchy light rain over the hills.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA dry and mostly sunny day,
OL,13,Fthough perhaps the chance for a little
OL,14,Flight rain on western hills during the
OL,15,Fmorning. Feeling fresher inland, but
OL,16,Fwarmer at the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
